HEADWORD: micturate
<hw>micturate</hw> <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>to pass urine through the
ureter; to urinate.</def> <mark>[Medical]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> urinate, piddle, puddle, piss, pee, pee-pee, make
water, relieve oneself, take a leak, spend a penny, wee, wee-wee, make,
pass water.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Micturition</ent>⟦br⟧
